=\n| location=[[Gondor]]\n| affiliation=\n| language=[[Westron]], [[Sindarin]]\n| birth={{TA|2480}}\n| birthlocation=\n| rule={{TA|2567}} - {{TA|2605|n}} (38 years)\n| death={{TA|2605}}\n| deathlocation=\n| age=125\n| notablefor=\n| house=[[House of Húrin]]\n| parentage=[[Cirion]]\n| siblings=\n| spouse=\n| children=[[Húrin II]]\n| gender=Male\n| height=\n| hair=\n| eyes=\n| clothing=\n| weapons=\n| steed=\n}}'''Hallas''' ([[Third Age]] 2480<ref>{{PM|Elendil}}, p. 205</ref> – 2605,<ref name=\"South\">{{App|South}}</ref> aged 125 years) was the thirteenth [[Ruling Steward]] of [[Gondor]].\n\n==History==\nHallas was the heir of [[Stewards|Steward]] [[Cirion]], who committed the rule of [[Minas Tirith]] to his son while Cirion led an army north to fight the [[Balchoth]] in {{TA|2510}}.  Following the unexpected victory at the [[Battle of the Field of Celebrant]], Hallas was a witness when Cirion gifted [[Calenardhon]] to [[Eorl|Eorl the Young]] and his people.<ref>{{UT|Cirion}}</ref>  In fact, it was Hallas who devised the names ''[[Rohan]]'' and ''[[Rohirrim]]''.<ref>{{UT|Index}}</ref>\n\nHallas died in {{TA|2605}} and was succeeded by his son, who became Steward [[Húrin II]].<ref name=\"South\"/>\n\n==Etymology==\n''Hallas'' is a [[Sindarin]] name. Its meaning is not glossed, but [[David Salo]] suggests that it means \"tallness\" and is a combination of ''hall'' (\"tall\") and the abstract ending ''-as''.<ref>{{HM|GS}}, p. 352</ref><ref>{{webcite|author=Paul Strack|articleurl=https://www.eldamo.org/content/words/word-3154390473.html|articlename=S. ''Hallas'' m.|website=Eldamo|accessed=12 August 2023}}</ref>\n\n==Genealogy==\n{{familytree/start}}\n{{familytree | BOR |BOR=[[Boromir (Steward of Gondor)|Boromir]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2410|n}} - {{TA|2489|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | CIR |CIR=[[Cirion]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2449|n}} - {{TA|2567|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | HAL |HAL='''HALLAS'''<br/><small>''{{TA|2480|n}} - {{TA|2605|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | HAL |HAL=[[Húrin II]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2515|n}} - {{TA|2628|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree | |!| |}}\n{{familytree | BEL |BEL=[[Belecthor I]]<br/><small>''{{TA|2545|n}} - {{TA|2655|n}}''</small>}}\n{{familytree/end}}\n\n{{References}}\n{{seq-start}}\n{{seq-head\n| race=gondorian\n| house=[[House of Húrin]]\n| born={{TA|2480}}\n| died={{TA|2605}}\n}}\n{{seq\n| prev=[[Cirion]]\n| list=13th [[Ruling Steward|Ruling Steward of Gondor]]\n| dates={{TA|2567}} - {{TA|2605|n}}\n| next=[[Húrin II]]\n}}\n{{seq-end}}\n{{rulingstewards}}\n[[Category:Gondorians]]\n[[Category:House of Húrin]]\n[[Category:Ruling stewards]]\n[[Category:Third Age characters]]\n\n[[de:Hallas]]\n[[fi:Hallas]]\n[[fr:encyclo:personnages:hommes:3a:dunedain:gondoriens:hallas]]"}}}